#include <iostream>
#include <cstdio>
using namespace std;

int t, A[4], B[4];

int main() {
	scanf("%d", &t);
	while (t--) {
		for (int i = 0; i < 4; i++)
			scanf("%d", &A[i]);
		for (int i = 0; i < 4; i++)
			scanf("%d", &B[i]);
		if (B[0] <= A[2] && B[1] <= A[3])
			printf("%d %d %d %d\n", B[0], A[1], A[2], B[3]);
		else
			printf("No Overlap\n");
	}
			
	return 0;
}
